        <title>Controls and Indicators</title>
        
        <levelledPara>
          <title>Structural Health Monitoring</title>
          <para>
            The Center Body is equipped with strain sensors and acoustic emission monitors 
            at critical load points. These sensors provide real-time structural health data 
            to the aircraft health monitoring system.
          </para>
        </levelledPara>
        
        <levelledPara>
          <title>Indicator Systems</title>
          <para>
            Visual inspection ports are provided at strategic locations to allow direct 
            observation of critical structural areas. Indicator marks on primary structure 
            show proper alignment and load distribution.
          </para>
        </levelledPara>
      </levelledPara>
